<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="boat-n">boat <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bəʊt/    美 /boʊt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>小船；艇：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>cross the river <strong>in a boat / by boat</strong> 
乘船过河</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-the-same-boat">in the same boat</h3>
<p>1.<strong>处境相同；面临同样的危险：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She and I are in the same boat: we both failed the exam. 
我和她同病相怜,考试都没及格。</p></div></div>